{"type":"freeform","cover":{"titleText":"","subTitleText":"","presenterText":"","dateText":"","logos":[]},"section":{"sectionText":"","smallerSectionText":""},"freeform":{"content":[[{"type":"text","span":3,"markdown":"OPD new cases >5 years show notable fluctuations but a strong upward trend overall, rising from ~150,000 per month in mid-2023 to nearly 190,000 per month by mid-2025.

OPD new cases <5 years remain comparatively stable, averaging 55,000–70,000 monthly, with smaller peaks in early and mid-2025.

